---
---

<section class="where section section-cream">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="where__heading reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Where We're Going</p>
      <h2>Three sites in active development across California, Nevada, and Texas.</h2>
      <p class="where__lede">
        Detailed pipeline available to <a class="where__nda-link" href="/investors">qualified investors under NDA</a>.
        More routes will follow. Subscribe to Field Notes for first access to site announcements,
        format openings, and the stories behind them.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="where__cta reveal">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/investors">
        Request investor briefing
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12" />
          <polyline points="13 6 19 12 13 18" />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://fieldnotes.rangewayev.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        Subscribe to Field Notes
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .where__heading {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-7);
  }

  .where__heading h2 {
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .where__lede {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    max-width: 68ch;
  }

  .where__nda-link {
    color: var(--color-warm-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .where__nda-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-warm-deep);
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .where__cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding-top: var(--space-6);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
</style>
